n Jiu-Jitsu For 'The Batman' |last=El-Mahmoud |first=Sarah |website=CinemaBlend |date=November 5, 2019 |access-date=November 6, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107032146/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2483898/robert-pattinson-is-training-in-jiu-jitsu-for-the-batman |archive-date=November 7, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BaleSupport\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christian-bale-robert-pattinson-good-choice-for-batman-watch-1203331841/ |title=Christian Bale: Robert Pattinson 'Good Choice' for Batman (Watch) |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=September 10, 2019 |access-date=September 29, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911124502/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christian-bale-robert-pattinson-good-choice-for-batman-watch-1203331841/ |archive-date=September 11, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BaleAdvice\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/robert-pattinson-batman-christian-bale-advice-dark-knight-matt-reeves-trailer-a9115206.html |title=Batman: Christian Bale shares advice for Robert Pattinson amid criticism over casting |last=Stolworthy |first=Jacob |website=[[The Independent]] |date=September 22, 2019 |access-date=September 29, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923235429/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/robert-pattinson-batman-christian-bale-advice-dark-knight-matt-reeves-trailer-a9115206.html |archive-date=September 23, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NolanAdvice\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/robert-pattinson-the-batman-lighthouse-joker-riddler-catwoman-173230182.html |title='The Batman' star Robert Pattinson on his 'cool' Batsuit, not facing Joaquin Phoenix's Joker and the horror of 'Lighthouse' flatulence |last=Alter |first=Ethan |website=[[Yahoo! News]] |date=October 18, 2019 |access-date=October 18, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/w